{
  "stem": "2353.2",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the only thing I found out from him was that when they got there, they were-- all their clothing was taken away from them, their underwear and everything.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They put them in striped prisoners' cotton uniforms.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they had to stay.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Now, Dachau is very high.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it gets very cold.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And this was in November.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They had to stand outside from 5 o'clock in the morning until 11 o'clock at night every day.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And when my father came out, he weighed 80 pounds.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So he signed himself into the Laupheim Hospital, which was run by Catholic nuns.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And the next day, the nuns came to him and said that you-- that he had to leave, because the authorities had told them he has to leave because he's Jewish.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he-- I think he went to a cousin's house to recuperate.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he was OK.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I think that his sudden death at the age of 66, I think, had something to do with what he went through.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I mean, not only the-- the concentration camp, but the whole process, what-- what happened to him with the factory, and fleeing, and all this kind of stuff.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I blame the Nazis for his death, too.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "What did he die of?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Had a very sudden heart attack, just, you know, 15 minutes and he was gone.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, nobody flew then.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was, you know, boat.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And there were a lot of other people on the boat that I knew.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it was kind of a fun time, if you didn't think back of that whom you left back and all this.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But it, you know, took about 10 days.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And it was OK.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "May something, 1937.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 8 SECONDS] And my brother was there at the pier, of course.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
